I’m bad at coding but if the future developerteam could explain some things to me, I could maybe learn the way of coding. I have a little bit experience with coding, I can’t fix errors myself and can’t do anything to a client yet. Ofcourse I know how to change starter pack,home,shops etc but different and/or advanced things like making a new skill is to hard for me now… I’m trying to learn the way of coding Project Insanity based servers so if you are interested in working with me, let me know!
